      <section eId="sec_445">
        <num>445</num>
        <heading>Order of support by relative; duration</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_445__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>If the court finds\nafter a hearing that a relative, including a step-parent, should be held\nresponsible under section four hundred fifteen for support, the court in\nits discretion may make an order requiring such person to contribute a\nfair and reasonable sum for the support of such person.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_445__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>For good cause shown, the court may at any time terminate or\nmodify an order made under this section.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
